## Host port mappings -------------------------------------------------
## Change ONLY the host side (left of the colon in docker-compose) if a
## port is already used on your machine. The most common conflict is
## FRONTEND_PORT=5173 versus a host-side `pnpm dev` server. Just pick
## another free port (e.g. 5273) and re-run `docker compose up -d`.
FRONTEND_PORT=5173
BACKEND_PORT=8000
MYSQL_PORT=3306
